@startuml handoff_lifecycle
' Diagram 3/5 — the handoff lifecycle: build -> describe -> re-validate -> extend.
' Source of truth: agora.plan.handoff, run_phased --phase0, runs 2.x / 3.

skinparam shadowing false

start
:Greenfield build (P3-P9)\nphase gates, one repair per gate;
:Extract FACT mechanically\nfile map + AST signatures,\ncapability inventory,\nverification record as COMPLETE\nre-runnable run_checks (**F20**);
note right
  FACT is never model-emitted:
  mechanically derivable facts
  hallucinate when generated
  (**F18-family** rationale)
end note
:PROSE via concrete micro-asks\n(3-8 lines each, anchored to\nspec/code — **F21**);
note right
  open-ended reflective asks derail
  (**F18‴**); concrete asks ran
  4/4 with zero reasoning-only
  turns (run 2.5)
end note
:Assemble PROJECT_STATE.md\n(deterministic, utf-8 pinned — **F20b**);
:Fact-check by RE-EXECUTION\n(chat-side; claims cite record);
:Tag baseline (echobot-vN);
partition "Brownfield entry (run 3)" {
  :RED-TEAM first: stale one source byte\n-> phase-0 MUST go red -> restore -> green;
  note right
    a protective gate is trusted only
    after it has been seen failing
  end note
  :phase-0: re-run the verification\nrecord's checks verbatim;
  :Extend via brief-as-index navigation:\ntask carries DELTA contract +\nmap-pointer only (**F22**);
  note right
    measured 3/3: model read the
    handoff first, opened only
    mapped files, never touched
    the frozen core signature
  end note
  :Old test suite rides along\nas free regression gate;
}
:Re-extract + reuse-staleness screen:\nevery REUSED prose section is re-asked\niff the delta touches its subject (**F24**);
:PROJECT_STATE.md vN+1 -> fact-check -> tag;
stop
@enduml
